Frederick Forsyth's Icon PART TWO: The manifesto of a new Russian presidential candidate has been found—a disturbing blueprint for returning his country to a military dictatorship. Only one ex-CIA operative is qualified to stop him and life and death fight to save the future of Russia and its people has begun.

Watch Part ONE here if you missed it!: https://youtu.be/F7qVp9tXkbg
